file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: "API"
  version: "1.0.0"
  contact:
    name: Starkina Maria
    email: starkina@surfstudio.ru

components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT 

security:
  - bearerAuth: []

paths:
  /billings/history:
    get:
      summary: История операций
      parameters:
        - $ref: "../common/resources/models.yaml#/components/parameters/limit"
        - $ref: "../common/resources/models.yaml#/components/parameters/offset"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: "Все ок"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "models.yaml#/components/schemas/HistoryResponse"
        default:
          $ref: "../common/errors.yaml#/components/responses/ApiErrorResponse"
